title: The 11th IFToMM International Symposium on Science of Mechanisms
description:
The 11th IFToMM International Symposium on Science of Mechanisms and Machines


ISBN: 3319018442 | 2013 | PDF | 528 pages | 16.6 MB

The general topic of the symposium follows mechanisms development through all stages of conception, modeling, analysis, synthesis and control to advanced product design. 

This volume brings together the latest results in the field and celebrates a series of conferences that has been running for 40 years. 

The contributors and the editor are world leaders in their field.
